# Stage 1 scope guard

This repository is a lightweight Stage 1 local YouTrack AI agent.

Do not introduce or enable by default unless explicitly requested and benchmark-justified:
- public deep/thinking modes
- streaming chain-of-thought or reasoning output
- always-on reranker
- critic pass by default
- multi-step LLM chains
- memory-based multi-turn LLM context
- heavy frontend rewrites
- Stage 2/3 machinery in active Stage 1 paths

When unsure, prefer:
- hidden
- disabled by default
- scaffold only